<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Tailscale Connection - iGreenMon</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
    <h2>New Tailscale Connection Established</h2>
    <p>Hi,</p>
    <p>
      A Tailscale connection has been established for your device.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 1rem 0; color: #555">
      <strong>Tailscale IP:</strong><br />
      <span style="color: #1a73e8"><%= ip %></span>
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 1rem 0; color: #555">
      <strong>MagicDNS Hostname:</strong><br />
      <a href="ssh://<%= hostname %>" target="_blank" style="color: #1a73e8"><%= hostname %></a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 2rem 0; color: #555">
      You can use the IP or hostname above to SSH into the device. Please ensure 
      your SSH key is configured and access is secured.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem">
      Kind regards,<br />
      The iGreenMon Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
